    {
        "content": "<p>I found this masters thesis by Max Lindh to be very helpful: <a href=\"http://uu.diva-portal.org/smash/record.jsf?pid=diva2%3A1184051&amp;dswid=5245\">http://uu.diva-portal.org/smash/record.jsf?pid=diva2%3A1184051&amp;dswid=5245</a></p>",
